<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>In 2018, HM Revenue and Customs’ leaders commissioned an independent review of what it’s like to work at <abbr title="HM Revenue and Customs">HMRC</abbr>.</p>

<p>The purpose of the report is to help <abbr title="HM Revenue and Customs">HMRC</abbr> become the values-driven and inclusive employer it’s committed to becoming.</p>

</div>
</div>

